            <title>[CASSANDRA-7508] nodetool prints error if dirs don&apos;t exist.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7508</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The new directory stuff blows up nodetool if its not there.  Like if I run nodetool from an different untar of the rc2 tar.gz.&lt;/p&gt;

